Package: clip-history
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6, libx11-6, libxfixes3, libwayland-client0, rofi
Maintainer: Anurag Sharma <anurag.iiitdm@gmail.com>
Description: A clipboard history engine.
 A lightweight clipboard history daemon and CLI engine written in pure C.
 Features ring buffer memory architecture, IPC UNIX sockets, and /dev/uinput virtual keystroke injection.
